contentrichtext.text: '''Indian Creek''' may refer to the following in the United States: {{tocright}} ==Communities== * [[Indian Creek, California]], unincorporated community in Calaveras County * [[Indian Creek, Florida]], village in Miami-Dade County * [[Indian Creek, Illinois]], village in Lake County * [[Indian Creek No. 7 Precinct, Menard County, Illinois]] * [[Indian Creek Township, White County, Illinois]] * [[Indian Creek, Texas]], town in Brown County * [[Indian Creek, Wisconsin]], unincorporated community in Polk County ==Streams== *[[Indian Creek (Boise River)]], tributary of the
